commit 48bb44b9aa52058bc8e97febc2a0fafa5d53624c
Author: Brian Waldon <bcwaldon@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Aug 29 08:55:20 2012 -0700

    Drop glance client + keystone config docs
    
